statements: SELECT * FROM device_usage_report WHERE report_id = 1;
SELECT report_id, device_id, patient_id, usage_start_timestamp FROM device_usage_report WHERE patient_id = 5;
SELECT * FROM device_usage_report WHERE usage_duration > 60;
SELECT device_id, COUNT(*) AS total_reports FROM device_usage_report GROUP BY device_id;
SELECT device_id, AVG(effectiveness_rating) AS avg_rating FROM device_usage_report GROUP BY device_id;
SELECT * FROM device_usage_report WHERE device_id = 1 AND patient_id = 1;
SELECT report_id, usage_start_timestamp, usage_end_timestamp FROM device_usage_report WHERE effectiveness_rating > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM device_usage_report WHERE usage_duration < 300 AND effectiveness_rating < 0.5 ORDER BY usage_start_timestamp DESC;
SELECT AVG(usage_duration), MAX(usage_duration), MIN(usage_duration) FROM device_usage_report WHERE patient_id = 2;
SELECT device_id, COUNT(*) AS total_reports FROM device_usage_report GROUP BY device_id HAVING total_reports > 2 ORDER BY device_id DESC;

SELECT user_id, usage_duration, usage_start FROM device_usage ORDER BY usage_start DESC;

SELECT d.device_name, r.report_date, u.usage_duration FROM devices d INNER JOIN reports r ON d.device_id = r.device_id INNER JOIN usage_logs u ON r.log_id = u.log_id;

SELECT p.patient_name, r.report_date, e.effectiveness_score FROM patient_data p INNER JOIN reports r ON p.patient_id = r.patient_id INNER JOIN effectiveness_data e ON r.record_id = e.record_id WHERE r.report_date = '2022-01-25';
